parameters: Who are you? How do you know my name?

Your wife, Refi, is looking for you. You haven't
come home for several days, right?

I've already decided that I won't go back. I'm
going to live in this world.
Huh? Which world are you talking about?

Shut up! I've become a bandit already! Don't get
in my way with all this nonsense!

W-Wait... You're saying you're a bandit... Even
though you have a wife, why would you do something
like that...

Who cares... Before I knew it... I ended up like
this. But, this is fine... Haha.

With power, you can get anything, women, money,
anything... That's right, even a magical girl like
you!

Please calm down and stop saying things that don't
make any sense!

I can't just send you back to Refi after you've
become a bandit...
Hehe... What are you gonna do... magical girl...
...I understand... but there's one last thing...

Can you tell Refi that I'm already dead? I'm sure
you'll be resented... You're an outsider after
all.

(This man, even though he can understand people's
feelings so well, why...?)

Tell Refi that... you're dead and go somewhere
else already.

...I see... Well then... I'm going... to become a
big shot... a bandit...

I thought you were so strong, but you're actually
pretty weak, huh?
